# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Only bad thing is we are traversing two times. which we can reduce to one by using "flag" boolean valriable rather than "break".
# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
