To get the max value, always try to make 9 the leftmost value, if its already 9, turn the 2nd to leftmost into a 9 and so on.
To get the max value, always try to make 0 the leftmost value, if its already 0, turn the 2nd to leftmost into a 0 and so on.


# Approach
To set the max value, search the leftmost digit that is not a 9 and change all those into 9s.

To set the min value, search the leftmost digit that is not a 0 and change all those into 0s.

Then substract both values.

